Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}害怕自己会从大家的心中消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.15,0:08:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.89,0:09:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}只属于自己的世界也会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.45,0:09:01.54,screen,NTP,0,0,0,,【害怕吧？】
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:03.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}自己会消失喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:04.54,screen,NTP,0,0,0,,【害怕吧？】
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不，我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}因为我想死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我想要的是绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我想回到虚无
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}可是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.96,0:09:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我无法回到虚无
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}那个人不让我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.48,0:09:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}还不愿让我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:25.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}因为那个人需要，我才存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不过结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.47,0:09:28.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不再需要我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.64,0:09:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}被他抛弃了，我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我明明一直祈祷这一天……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}但，现在却很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}来，走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.74,0:09:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}你就是为了今天，为了这一天而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}丽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}是
