Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}错了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.39,0:10:34.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}并不是重归于虚无
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}只不过是让一切回归起点
