Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.85,0:11:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}所以要帮助妈妈，我必须当好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.54,0:12:01.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}可是我不想变成妈妈那样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}爸爸不在的时候妈妈总是哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我不可以哭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不可以撒娇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.64,0:12:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}所以我一定要做好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}要不被爸爸讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:16.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不过我讨厌爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}因此我讨厌好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.02,0:12:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.85,0:12:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我已经累了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不管是维持自己的纯洁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}还是继续装纯洁的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我已经累了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我想被玷污
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我想看看被玷污的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.41,0:12:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}所以让那个男人拥抱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我是喜欢他…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.48,0:12:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}才让他拥抱的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}真的喜欢他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}对，没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}他接受了真实的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:48.76,screen,NTP,0,0,0,,【真的吗？】
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.23,0:12:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)\fs32}他很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不要
