Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.19,0:13:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}如今还有什么好害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}当然害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}为什么会觉得羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}在喜欢的男人面前你明明很自然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.15,0:13:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不，应该说很乐意摆出这副模样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}给真嗣看到这个样子你明明很高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.14,0:13:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}胡说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:29.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,550)fs32}不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.63,0:13:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}你明明很想给父亲看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}你在加持的睡脸上面寻求自己的平静
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.91,0:13:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}在加持的温柔当中寻求自己的平静
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.11,0:13:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}在加持的怀抱当中寻求父亲的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我在加持身上找到了自己的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.01,0:14:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}所以我逃走了，逃离他的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.43,0:14:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}简直就像跟爸爸在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}可是我其实很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}那成为一种快感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}是心情好得不得了的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}所以我不想那样了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}所以我跟他分手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}也就是说恋爱的开始虽然没有理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}结束却有理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}你真温柔，加持
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}用你的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.94,0:14:34.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,350)\fs34}玷污我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.76,0:14:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}就算现在很讨厌自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.16,0:14:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}也不该自我伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}那只不过，是给自己刹那的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.13,0:14:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}用来敷衍自己罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}你最好别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:51.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}那，你是叫我好好爱惜自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}男人都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.29,0:14:58.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}然后就一头钻进工作或自己的世界里面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:15:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}把我就这样丢在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}跟爸爸一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:06.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}你只是一味地逃避痛苦的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}痛苦的现实…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.27,0:15:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}是在说我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}确实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.11,0:15:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我就是这种人，没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.46,0:15:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,550)\fs32}别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}美里小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.26,0:15:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我常常对自己感到绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}觉得自己很恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不检点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}真是肮脏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.05,0:15:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}太难看了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}下流
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}肮脏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}没想到这就是成年人的交往，真让人恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.69,0:15:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}恭喜你晋升，葛城少校
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}大家所认同的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}是为得到认同而演戏的那个我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不是真正的自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}真正的自己却一直在哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不，我是幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:48.73,screen,NTP,0,0,0,,【我是幸福的吗？】
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)\fs32}我是幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:51.90,screen,NTP,0,0,0,,【我是幸福的吗？】
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.15,0:15:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)\fs34}我是幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:54.74,screen,NTP,0,0,0,,【我是幸福的吗？】
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.06,0:15:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,550)\fs35}不对，这并不是幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:15:58.45,screen,NTP,0,0,0,,【幸福是什么？】
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:16:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}这不是真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.47,0:16:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)\fs32}我只是这么深信罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:06.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不这么做我们就活不下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.47,0:16:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}没人在一起的话会感到害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.45,0:16:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}觉得不安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.83,0:16:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}没有人睡在身边的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.10,0:16:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}你害怕一个人睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}果然还是一个人睡会寂寞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}她是忍受不了心里的失落感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.30,0:16:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}所以和谁都无所谓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.15,0:16:23.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我只是想沉溺在简单的快乐当中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}只是想用刹那间的逃避治疗内心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}所以我只是在利用男人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.66,0:16:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)\fs32}不对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.86,0:16:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,550)\fs33}不对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:40.33,screen,NTP,0,0,0,,【她到底在期望什么？】
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:41.45,screen,NTP,0,0,0,,【Case 2】
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.11,0:16:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}这是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}这是明日香心中的我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}也就是说，同时是真嗣心中的我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.46,0:16:53.92,screen,NTP,0,0,0,,【{\fnEVA-FANS方正粗宋v3}惣{\r}流·明日香·兰利的情况 （Part 1）】
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}明日香在祈求什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:16:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我要一个人活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不需要爸爸和妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}一个人活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我再也不会哭泣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.45,0:17:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}可是，我还是在哭着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.89,0:17:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}为什么哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我不太会应付那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}这么没信心不像做医生的你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}医生也是人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}以前我就和你说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.84,0:17:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}可是像你这样的女性怎会应付不了一个小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}她出奇地成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}又一副拒人千里的态度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.64,0:17:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我常常觉得害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.74,0:17:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}老公你没有这种感觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.54,0:17:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.84,0:17:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}反正你已经是明日香的母亲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}但我首先是你的妻子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.03,0:17:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}同时发生的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.27,0:17:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}对，从社会的角度来看确实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.82,0:17:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}虽然你没办法不做那孩子的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.01,0:17:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我却可随时不做她的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:17:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}话是这么说没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:17:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不要啊！妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不要不做我的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.62,0:18:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我会做个妈妈喜欢的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}所以请不要不做我的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.57,0:18:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,350)\fs32}所以请看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不要啊妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不要杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}你爸爸讨厌妈妈了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不要妈妈了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:19.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}一定是从一开始就不喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}一定是从一开始就不想要我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}所以跟妈妈一起死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}爸爸已经不要我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.20,0:18:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我很碍事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不要我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.56,0:18:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}跟～我～一～起～死～吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}不要！我不是妈妈的洋娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.31,0:18:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}我要自己思考，自己活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}那时候，妈妈吊在天花板上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}脸上看起来非常愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}可是，我非常讨厌那个表情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.35,0:18:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}讨厌死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}讨厌自己的消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.40,0:18:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}讨厌男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.22,0:19:01.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}讨厌爸爸、妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.46,0:19:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}讨厌所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}没有人愿意保护我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}都不愿意待在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:10.43,screen,NTP,0,0,0,,【她期待的是什么？】
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}所以我要一个人活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(050,050)}可是我讨厌这样，很痛苦啊
